of 37,5mg, 75mg N30 </p>\r\n<p>Nootropics</p>\r\n<p>Aminolon (Gamma-aminobutyric acid*) tablets of 250mg N50, N100 <br />\r\n Phenibut (Phenibut*) tablets of 250mg N20<br />\r\n Piracetam (Piracetam*) a solution of 200 mg/ml 5ml N10</p>\r\n<p>A preparation for treating of gout</p>\r\n<p>Allopurinol (Allopurinol*) tablets of 100mg N50, 300 mg N30</p>\r\n<p>Vitamins</p>\r\n<p>Nicotinic acid (Acid Nicotinic*) a solution of 10 mg/ml 1ml N10</p>", "ENGLISH", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "820-revision-v1", "", "", "2018-04-20 17:25:07", "2018-04-20 10:25:07", "", "820", "http://organica-nk.ru/820-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
